    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Multiple-word terms or names that are arranged in the form used in back-of-book indexing or other similar situations. Examples are Wren, Christopher and buttresses, flying. Distinguished from natural order terms or names.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
